title: 50 Million Instagrammers Follow Taylor Swift for Her #039;Cute Cats#039;
text:
Get Entertainment Alerts 
9 Oct 2015 06:36 AM EST 
It’s official: Taylor Swift is the new Queen of Instagram. The “Wildest Dreams” singer collected 50 million followers on Thursday. Reaching the 50 million mark makes her profile the most popular account on the photo-sharing platform. Swift noted the milestone by posting, "50 million followers! I’m pretty sure this is just because I have cute cats, though.” As Celebuzz previously reported, Swift beat out two social media titans for the top honor: Kim Kardashian, who currently has 48.4 million followers, and Beyoncé, who has 47.5 million followers.
